attributes.review: Mr Krabs operating costs would be 10,400, now let's quickly find his monthly earnings. 34,575.01 - 12,400 = 22,175.01 Mr Krabs Monthly Earnings from the Krusty Krab would 22,175.01, now we take this and find his yearly revenue. 22,175.01 x 12 = 266,100.12 Mr Krabs yearly earnings from the Krusty Krab would be 266,100.12, now we’ll be saying that each season of spongebob is a passing year. This will help us find his lifetime earnings from the Krusty Krab, this will be our final math portion so let's finish off strong. 266,100.12 x 11 = $2,927,101.32 So officially by the shows standards, Mr Krabs has earned over 2 million dollars and has that money to his name. How do I know this? Well because this app mad my phone glitch so I had to resort to mathematics
